#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:9
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced Editing Tools"
msgstr "Ferramentas de edición avanzada"

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid "Comment/Uncomment"
msgstr "Comentarios de código"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:15
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The Comment and Uncomment commands, available from the <guimenu>Tools</"
#| "guimenu> menu allow you to add or remove comment markers to the "
#| "selection, or the current line if no text is selected, if comments are "
#| "supported by the format of the text you are editing."
msgid ""
"The <guimenuitem>Comment</guimenuitem> and <guimenuitem>Uncomment</"
"guimenuitem> commands, available from the <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> menu "
"allow you to add or remove comment markers to the selection, or the current "
"line if no text is selected, if comments are supported by the format of the "
"text you are editing."
msgstr ""
"As ordes «Comentar» e «Descomentar», dispoñibeis no menú "
"<guimenu>Utilidades</guimenu>, permiten engadir ou retirar marcas de "
"comentario do texto seleccionado —ou da liña actual se non se seleccionou "
"nada— nos casos nos que o formato do texto que se está a editar permite o "
"uso de comentarios."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The rules for how commenting is done are defined in the syntax definitions, "
"so if syntax highlighting is not used, commenting/uncommenting is not "
"possible."
msgstr ""
"As regras para comentar e descomentar defínense nas definicións da sintaxe, "
"así que en caso de non usar o realzado da sintaxe, a funcionalidade de "
"comentar e descomentar non estará dispoñíbel."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some formats define single line comment markers, some multiline markers and "
"some both. If multiline markers are not available, commenting out a "
"selection that does not fully include its last line is not possible."
msgstr ""
"Algúns formatos definen marcas de comentarios dunha liña, outros de "
"comentarios de varias liñas, e outros dispoñen de ambos os dous tipos de "
"comentarios. Nos casos nos que non se dispoña de marcas de comentarios de "
"varias liñas, non será posíbel comentar un texto seleccionado que non inclúa "
"a totalidade das liñas que abrangue."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a single line marker is available, commenting single lines is preferred "
"where applicable, as this helps to avoid problems with nested comments."
msgstr ""
"Cando haxa dispoñibeis marcas de comentarios dunha soa liña, usaranse ditas "
"marcas cando sexa posíbel, dado que os comentarios dunha soa liña axudan a "
"evitar problemas coa aniñación de comentarios."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When removing comment markers, no uncommented text should be selected. When "
"removing multiline comment markers from a selection, any whitespace outside "
"the comment markers is ignored."
msgstr ""
"Ao retirar marcas de comentarios, non debería seleccionarse texto que non "
"dispoña de tales. Ao retirar marcadores de comentarios de varias liñas dunha "
"selección, calquera espazo en branco fóra das marcas de comentario "
"ignorarase."

#. Tag: primary
#: advanced.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>comment</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>comentar</primary>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:38
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To place comment markers, use the <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Comment</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item or the "
#| "related keyboard shortcut sequence, default is <keycombo action=\"simul"
#| "\">&Ctrl;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo>."
msgid ""
"To place comment markers, use the <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Comment</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item or the "
"related keyboard shortcut sequence, the default is <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Para engadir marcas de comentario, empregue <menuchoice><guimenu>Utilidades</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Comentar</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ou o atallo de "
"teclado correspondente. O atallo predeterminado é <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: primary
#: advanced.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>uncomment</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>descomentar</primary>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:44
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To remove comment markers, use the <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Uncomment</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item or "
#| "the related keyboard shortcut, default is <keycombo action=\"simul"
#| "\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo>."
msgid ""
"To remove comment markers, use the <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Uncomment</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item or the "
"related keyboard shortcut, the default is <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"&Shift;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Para retirar marcas de comentario, empregue <menuchoice><guimenu>Utilidades</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Descomentar</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ou o atallo de "
"teclado correspondente. O atallo predeterminado é <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Editor Component Command Line"
msgstr "A liña de ordes do compoñente de edición"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:55
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kappname;'s editor component has an internal command line, allowing you "
#| "to perform various actions from a minimal GUI. The command line is a text "
#| "entry in the bottom of the editor area, to show it select "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Switch to Command Line</"
#| "guimenuitem></menuchoice> or use the shortcut (default is <keycombo "
#| "action=\"simul\"><keycap>F7</keycap></keycombo>). The editor provides a "
#| "set of commands as documented below, and additional commands can be "
#| "provided by plugins."
msgid ""
"&kappname;'s editor component has an internal command line, allowing you to "
"perform various actions from a minimal &GUI;. The command line is a text "
"entry at the bottom of the editor area; to show it select "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Switch to Command Line</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> or use the shortcut (default is <keycombo action="
"\"simul\"><keycap>F7</keycap></keycombo>). The editor provides a set of "
"commands as documented below, and additional commands can be provided by "
"plugins."
msgstr ""
"O compoñente de edición de &kappname; conta cunha liña de ordes interna, o "
"que permite levar a cabo varias accións desde unha interface gráfica mínima. "
"A liña de ordes consiste nun campo de texto na parte inferior da zona de "
"edición, que pode amosarse desde <menuchoice><guimenu>Vista</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Cambiar á liña de ordes</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ou "
"mediante o atallo de teclado correspondente (<keycombo action=\"simul"
"\"><keycap>F7</keycap></keycombo> é o predeterminado). O editor fornece unha "
"serie de ordes de seu —listadas a continuación—, e a lista de ordes "
"dispoñibeis pode estenderse mediante complementos."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To execute a command, type the command then press the return key. The "
"command line will indicate whether it succeeded and possibly display a "
"message. If you entered the command line by pressing <keycap>F7</keycap> it "
"will automatically hide after a few seconds. To clear the message and enter "
"a new command, press <keycap>F7</keycap> again."
msgstr ""
"Para executar unha orde, introdúzaa no campo de texto e prema a tecla Intro. "
"A liña de ordes indicará se a orde se executou correctamente, e posibelmente "
"amose unha mensaxe. Se accedeu á liña de ordes mediante o atallo de teclado "
"(<keycap>F7</keycap>), esta agocharase automaticamente despois duns "
"segundos. Para retirar a mensaxe e inserir unha nova orde, volva usar o "
"atallo de teclado."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:70
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The command line has a built-in help system, issue the command "
#| "<command>help</command> to get started. To see a list of all available "
#| "commands issue <command>help list</command>, to view help for a specific "
#| "command, do <command>help <replaceable>command</replaceable></command>."
msgid ""
"The command line has a built-in help system; issue the command "
"<command>help</command> to get started. To see a list of all available "
"commands issue <command>help list</command>; to view help for a specific "
"command, do <command>help <replaceable>command</replaceable></command>."
msgstr ""
"A liña de ordes conta cun sistema de axuda integrado. Execute a orde "
"<command>help</command>; aparecerá unha mensaxe cunha pequena introdución á "
"liña de ordes de &kappname; e o sue sistema de axuda. Para obter unha lista "
"das ordes dispoñibeis, execute <command>help list</command>, e para obter "
"axuda sobre unha orde concreta, execute <command>help <replaceable>orde</"
"replaceable></command>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:75
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The command line has a built in history, so you can reuse commands "
#| "already typed. To navigate the history, use the <keycap>Up</keycap> and "
#| "<keycap>Down</keycap> keys. When showing historical commands, the "
#| "argument part of the command will be selected, allowing you to easily "
#| "overwrite the arguments."
msgid ""
"The command line has a built in history, so you can reuse commands already "
"typed. To navigate the history, use the &Up; and &Down; keys. When showing "
"historical commands, the argument part of the command will be selected, "
"allowing you to easily overwrite the arguments."
msgstr ""
"A liña de ordes ten ademais un historial integrado que permite reusar ordes "
"empregadas anteriormente. Para examinar o historial, empregue as teclas "
"<keycap>↑</keycap> and <keycap>↓</keycap>. Ao escoller unha orde do "
"historial, a parte dos argumentos seleccionarase de maneira automática, "
"permitindo cambiar estes facilmente."

