#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "Argument types"
msgstr "Tipos de argumento"

#. Tag: term
#: advanced.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "BOOLEAN"
msgstr "BOOLEANO"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is used with commands that turns things on or off. Legal values are "
"<userinput>on</userinput>, <userinput>off</userinput>, <userinput>true</"
"userinput>, <userinput>false</userinput>, <userinput>1</userinput> or "
"<userinput>0</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Empregado con ordes que activan ou desactivan cousas. Os seus posíbeis "
"valores son: <userinput>on</userinput>, <userinput>off</userinput>, "
"<userinput>true</userinput>, <userinput>false</userinput>, <userinput>1</"
"userinput> ou <userinput>0</userinput>."

#. Tag: term
#: advanced.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "INTEGER"
msgstr "ENTEIRO"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "An integer number."
msgstr "Un número enteiro."

#. Tag: term
#: advanced.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "STRING"
msgstr "CADEA"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A string, surrounded by single quotes (') or double quotes (\") when it "
"contains spaces."
msgstr ""
"Unha cadea, delimitada por comiñas simples (') ou dobres (\") cando contén "
"espazos."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "Commands for Configuring the Editor"
msgstr "Ordes para configurar o editor"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:112
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "These commands are provided by the editor component, and allows you to "
#| "configure the active document and view only. This is handy if you want to "
#| "use a setting different from the default settings, for example for "
#| "indentation."
msgid ""
"These commands are provided by the editor component, and allow you to "
"configure the active document and view only. This is handy if you want to "
"use a setting different from the default settings, for example for "
"indentation."
msgstr ""
"As seguintes ordes permiten configurar o documento e vista activos con "
"independencia dos demais. Resultan útiles cando se quere empregar unha "
"configuración diferente da predeterminada, por exemplo para o sangrado."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
