"Usar o valor <userinput>anchura</userinput> para a anchura das tabulacións."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>set-indent-width</command><arg choice=\"req\">INTEGER width</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>set-indent-width</command><arg choice=\"req\">ENTEIRO anchura</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the indentation width to the number <userinput>width</userinput>. Used "
"only if you are indenting with spaces."
msgstr ""
"Usar o valor <userinput>anchura</userinput> para a anchura do sangrado. Só "
"ten efecto ao usar espazos para o sangrado."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
