"<command>set-folding-markers</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEANO activar</"
"arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sets the visibility of the folding markers pane."
msgstr "Define a visibilidade do panel dos marcadores de pregado."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>set-line-numbers</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEAN enable</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>set-line-numbers</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEANO activar</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sets the visibility of the line numbers pane."
msgstr "Determina a visibilidade do panel dos números de liña."

# skip-rule: trasno-tab
#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>set-replace-tabs</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEAN enable</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>set-replace-tabs</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEANO activar</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid "If enabled, tabs are replaced with spaces as you type."
msgstr ""
"Ao activarse (on), as tabulacións substituiranse por espazos a medida que se "
"escriban."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>set-remove-trailing-space</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEAN "
"enable</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>set-remove-trailing-space</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEANO "
"activar</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:162
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If enabled, trailing whitespace are removed whenever the cursor leaves a "
#| "line."
msgid ""
"If enabled, trailing whitespace is removed whenever the cursor leaves a line."
msgstr ""
"Ao activarse (on), os espazos (innecesarios) á dereita da liña na que estea "
"o cursor eliminaranse cando o cursor cambie a outra liña."

# skip-rule: trasno-tab
#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>set-show-tabs</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEAN enable</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>set-show-tabs</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEANO activar</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If enabled, TAB characters and trailing whitespace will be visualized by a "
"small dot."
msgstr ""
"Ao activarse (on), as tabulacións e os espazos innecesarios representaranse "
"con pequenos puntos."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>set-show-indent</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEAN enable</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>set-show-indent</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEANO activar</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid "If enabled, indentation will be visualized by a vertical dotted line."
msgstr ""
"Ao activarse (on), o sangrado representarase cunha liña de puntos vertical."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>set-indent-spaces</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEAN enable</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>set-indent-spaces</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEANO activar</"
"arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If enabled, the editor will indent with <option>indent-width</option> spaces "
"for each indentation level, rather than with one TAB character."
msgstr ""
"Ao activarse (on), o editor usará a cantidade de espazos definida na opción "
"<option>indent-width</option> para cada nivel de sangrado, en vez dunha "
"tabulación."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>set-mixed-indent</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEAN enable</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>set-mixed-indent</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEANO activar</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If enabled, &kappname; will use a mix of TAB and spaces for indentation. "
"Each indentation level will be <option>indent-width</option> wide, and more "
"indentation levels will be optimized to use as many TAB characters as "
"possible."
msgstr ""
"Ao activarse (on), &kappname; usará unha mestura de tabulacións e espazos "
"para o sangrado. Cada nivel de sangrado terá unha anchura equivalente ao "
"valor da opción <option>indent-width</option>, e os sucesivos niveis de "
"sangrado optimizaranse para usar cantas tabulacións sexan posíbeis. Por "
"exemplo, se <option>indent-width</option> vale «2», e as tabulacións están "
"configuradas para ter unha anchura de «4»: 1 nivel de sangrado equivalerá a "
"dous espazos, 2 niveis equivalerán a unha tabulación, e 3 niveis equivalerán "
"a unha tabulación seguida de dous espazos."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When executed, this command will additionally set space indentation enabled, "
"and if the indent width is unspecified it will be set to half of the "
"<option>tab-width</option> for the document at the time of execution."
msgstr ""
"Ao executarse esta orde, activarase automaticamente o sangrado con espazos, "
"e en caso de non estar definida a anchura de sangrado, daráselle como valor "
"a metade do valor da propiedade <option>tab-width</option> do documento "
"activo no momento de execución da orde."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>set-word-wrap</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEAN enable</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>set-word-wrap</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEANO activar</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:199
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Enables dynamic word wrap according to <userinput>enable</userinput>"
msgid "Enables dynamic word wrap according to <userinput>enable</userinput>."
msgstr "Activa (on) ou desactiva (off) a división visual das liñas."

# skip-rule: trasno-tab
#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>set-replace-tabs-save</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEAN enable </"
"arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>set-replace-tabs-save</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEANO "
"activar</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When enabled, tabs will be replaced with whitespace whenever the document is "
"saved."
msgstr ""
"Ao activarse (on), as tabulacións substituiranse por espazos cada vez que se "
"garde o documento."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>set-remove-trailing-space-save</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEAN "
"enable</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>set-remove-trailing-space-save</command><arg choice=\"req"
"\">BOOLEANO activar</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When enabled, trailing space will be removed from each line whenever the "
"document is saved."
msgstr ""
"Ao activarse (on), os espazos (innecesarios) á dereita de cada liña "
"retiraranse ao gardar o documento."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>set-indent-mode</command><arg choice=\"req\">STRING name</arg>"
msgstr "<command>set-indent-mode</command><arg choice=\"req\">CADEA nome</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the autoindentation mode to <userinput>name</userinput>. If "
"<userinput>name</userinput> is not known, the mode is set to 'none'. Valid "
"modes are 'none', 'normal', 'cstyle', 'haskell', 'lilypond', 'lisp', "
"'python', 'ruby' and 'xml'."
msgstr ""
"Cambia o modo de sangrado automático ao <userinput>nome</userinput>. O "
"seguintes son os valores correctos para o argumento <userinput>nome</"
"userinput>: «none» (desactivación do sangrado automático), «normal», "
"«cstyle» (sangrado de C), «haskell», «lilypond», «lisp», «python», «ruby» e "
"«xml». Se non se recoñece o valor de <userinput>nome</userinput>, "
"desactivarase o sangrado automático."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>set-auto-ident</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEAN script</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>set-auto-ident</command><arg choice=\"req\">BOOLEANO activar</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable or disable autoindentation."
msgstr "Activar ou desactivar o sangrado automático."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: advanced.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>set-highlight</command><arg choice=\"req\">STRING highlight</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>set-highlight</command><arg choice=\"req\">CADEA realzado</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the syntax highlighting system for the document. The argument must be a "
"valid highlight name, as seen in the <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Highlighting</guisubmenu></menuchoice> menu. This "
"command provides an autocompletion list for its argument."
msgstr ""
"Definir o sistema de realzado da sintaxe para o documento actual. O "
"argumento debe ser un nome correcto de realzado no menú "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Utilidades</guimenu><guisubmenu>Realzado</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice>. A orde fornece unha función de completado automático para o "
"argumento <userinput>realzado</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:240
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Reload all <link linkend=\"advanced-editing-tools-scripting\">JavaScript "
#| "scripts</link> used by Kate, including indenters and command line scripts."
